"STATEMENT OF PURPOSE

1. To reawaken an awareness of spiritual values in daily life.

2. To promote planetary awareness, which leads to planetary citizenship. This includes an awareness of the underlying energy structure of our society, the kingdoms of nature, the planet and the solar system.

3. To analyze and help solve world problems on the basis of spiritual values and planetary awareness, thus meeting true present needs."
